7
00:00:16,670 --> 00:00:19,360
Dr. Ling not only has good medical skills
but also charges low fees.

8
00:00:19,360 --> 00:00:20,630
We're willing to wait a bit longer.

9
00:00:20,630 --> 00:00:21,860
- Really?
- Yes.

10
00:00:22,150 --> 00:00:23,150
Ma'am.

11
00:00:23,150 --> 00:00:24,480
Follow this prescription

12
00:00:24,480 --> 00:00:25,670
and take it three times a day.

13
00:00:25,670 --> 00:00:27,360
It will help relieve your

14
00:00:27,360 --> 00:00:28,500
cold and cough symptoms.

15
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:35,940
Doctor, here's the payment.

16
00:00:38,110 --> 00:00:39,420
One is enough.

17
00:00:39,990 --> 00:00:41,360
Thank you, Dr. Ling.

18
00:00:41,360 --> 00:00:42,290
You're welcome.

19
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:45,800
Remember to take your medicine on time.

20
00:00:45,800 --> 00:00:46,730
Okay.

21
00:00:46,730 --> 00:00:48,720
(Chunfeng Clinic)

22
00:00:48,720 --> 00:00:49,260
