26
00:00:53,720 --> 00:00:54,600
Yes.

27
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:57,150
We haven't had any patients
for several days.

28
00:00:57,150 --> 00:00:58,030
At this rate,

29
00:00:58,030 --> 00:01:00,590
