30
00:01:00,590 --> 00:01:01,540
Yes.

31
00:01:03,780 --> 00:01:05,380
(Three days ago)

32
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:09,280
Recently,
Capital Physicians' Guild income has plummeted,

33
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:11,330
falling to less than 30%
of what it used to be.

34
00:01:11,330 --> 00:01:12,253
(Wang Baoshan,)
Wang Baoshan.

35
00:01:12,277 --> 00:01:13,890
(President of the Physicians' Guild)
Wang Baoshan.

36
00:01:13,890 --> 00:01:14,400
You are so bold,

37
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,590
daring to embezzle my money.

38
00:01:15,590 --> 00:01:16,960
I dare not, Your Highness.

39
00:01:16,960 --> 00:01:18,670
The Physicians' Guild is your property.

40
00:01:18,670 --> 00:01:20,070
How could I have the audacity

41
00:01:20,070 --> 00:01:22,190
to covet your money?

42
00:01:22,190 --> 00:01:25,030
It's just a new clinic opened
in the capital

43
