to be the president?

49
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:37,980
Your Highness, please calm down.

50
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:40,360
I will handle it right away.

51
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:41,440
Right away.

52
00:01:41,440 --> 00:01:42,540
Right away. Right away.

53
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:55,130
You are the new doctor?

54
00:01:56,750 --> 00:01:58,510
Yes, who are you?

55
00:02:02,550 --> 00:02:05,730
I am the president
of the Capital Physicians' Guild.

56
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:08,810
Since you have opened a clinic
in the capital city,

57
00:02:09,670 --> 00:02:12,320
