81
00:03:06,670 --> 00:03:08,940
I'll see how you can establish yourself
in the capital city.

82
00:03:17,190 --> 00:03:18,130
President.

83
00:03:18,550 --> 00:03:20,720
Chunfeng Clinic not only
refuses to raise its prices,

84
