we're all going to be doomed.

86
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:26,230
You have to figure out a solution.

87
00:03:26,230 --> 00:03:27,240
Yes.

88
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:30,280
A small clinic with no background

89
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,980
