90
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:34,650
I will definitely teach it a lesson.

91
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:38,650
My Lord.

92
00:03:38,880 --> 00:03:39,720
My Lord.

93
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,630
Greetings, My Lord.

94
00:03:41,630 --> 00:03:42,980
You trash.

95
00:03:42,980 --> 00:03:45,400
(Xie Nanyuan, heir of Marquis Zhennan)
I've taken so much of your medicine,

96
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:47,110
but it hasn't had any effect at all.

97
00:03:47,110 --> 00:03:48,400
You can close your clinic.

98
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,250
Smash it!

99
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:51,920
Please calm down.

100
00:03:51,920 --> 00:03:54,230
Even the imperial physicians
can't cure your illness.

101
00:03:54,230 --> 00:03:56,030
