102
00:03:56,030 --> 00:03:57,110
Please forgive us.

103
00:03:57,110 --> 00:03:58,610
In your dreams!

104
00:03:59,190 --> 00:04:01,100
If I die,

105
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:03,540
I'll take you all with me.

106
00:04:05,670 --> 00:04:06,860
The pain is killing me.

107
00:04:10,190 --> 00:04:11,760
I have an idea.

108
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:13,920
I've heard that Dr. Ling
of Chunfeng Clinic

109
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:16,030
