a miracle-working doctor

110
00:04:16,030 --> 00:04:19,470
and boasts that there is no disease
that she cannot cure.

111
00:04:19,470 --> 00:04:22,670
You can go and give it a try.

112
00:04:22,670 --> 00:04:24,290
What are you waiting for?

113
00:04:24,510 --> 00:04:25,940
Take me there.

114
