in the military.

118
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:43,330
Even His Majesty needs to respect him.

119
00:04:43,670 --> 00:04:46,290
His son's status is as prestigious
as that of a prince.

120
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:49,980
Ling Ruojin will be in big trouble.

121
00:04:52,590 --> 00:04:54,550
God is on my side.

122
00:04:54,550 --> 00:04:55,420
Yes.

123
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:02,990
Where is Dr. Ling?

124
00:05:02,990 --> 00:05:04,230
I'm a lord. Come out.

125
00:05:04,230 --> 00:05:05,290
Someone is going to die here.

126
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,730
Come and sit over here.

127
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:13,250
Jesus.

128
00:05:13,550 --> 00:05:14,650
Are you kidding me?

129
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:16,960
I'm looking for a doctor.

130
00:05:16,960 --> 00:05:18,540
