133
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:24,860
What do women know about medicine?

134
00:05:25,150 --> 00:05:27,250
And you boast about yourself.

135
00:05:27,550 --> 00:05:28,500
Guards.

136
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,590
Smash this clinic.

137
00:05:30,590 --> 00:05:31,810
- Yes.
- Hold on.

138
00:05:32,630 --> 00:05:33,580
