from a blockage in the appendix.

148
00:05:58,190 --> 00:05:59,240
Appendix?

149
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,080
Inflammation?

150
00:06:00,100 --> 00:06:01,730
What are all these things?

151
00:06:04,590 --> 00:06:05,540
Yes.

152
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:07,190
What are these things?

153
00:06:07,190 --> 00:06:08,840
I've never heard of them.

154
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:10,420
You must be lying to me.

155
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:11,650
Smash this clinic.

156
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,320
Just because you haven't heard of it,

157
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:14,770
doesn't mean it doesn't exist.

158
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:18,650
Your symptoms aren't serious.

159
00:06:19,150 --> 00:06:20,030
Take some medicine

160
00:06:20,030 --> 00:06:21,650
to reduce the inflammation
and you will be fine.

161
00:06:27,250 --> 00:06:28,090
Okay.

162
00:06:28,440 --> 00:06:29,460
Give me the medicine quickly.

163
00:06:29,670 --> 00:06:30,860
Reduce the inflammation, right?

164
00:06:31,190 --> 00:06:32,130
Do it.

165
00:06:34,550 --> 00:06:35,500
Give me your hand.

166
00:06:48,610 --> 00:06:49,480
How do you feel?

167
00:06:55,400 --> 00:06:56,500
It doesn't hurt anymore.

168
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:59,190
What I gave you

169
00:06:59,190 --> 00:07:01,020
