170
00:07:01,590 --> 00:07:05,020
This is the anti-inflammatory drug.

171
00:07:05,020 --> 00:07:06,400
(Anti-inflammatory Drug)
Take it back.

172
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:07,550
Use it three times a day,

173
00:07:07,550 --> 00:07:09,110
one pill each time.

174
00:07:09,110 --> 00:07:10,250
You'll be healed

175
00:07:10,670 --> 00:07:12,250
in about three days.

176
00:07:13,110 --> 00:07:14,460
I didn't expect that

177
