178
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,170
My Lord.

179
00:07:20,960 --> 00:07:23,980
Do you have pain

180
00:07:24,320 --> 00:07:25,720
and blood in your stools?

181
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:27,110
Good for you.

182
00:07:27,110 --> 00:07:28,610
How did you see that?

183
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:36,020
