185
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:40,730
No need.

186
00:07:42,990 --> 00:07:44,000
Here you go.

187
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,510
Take one in the morning
and one in the evening.

188
00:07:45,510 --> 00:07:46,940
It'll take immediate effect.

189
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:55,290
