202
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:41,480
Three...

203
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:44,070
I have already said

204
00:08:44,070 --> 00:08:45,570
I am not interested.

205
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:49,170
300 taels per month.

206
00:08:50,430 --> 00:08:53,780
Your clinic can't make
that much money in a year.

207
00:08:54,520 --> 00:08:55,560
My Lord.

208
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:57,310
Take this money back.

209
00:08:57,310 --> 00:08:58,560
I'm busy.

210
00:08:58,560 --> 00:09:00,370
Goodbye, My Lord.

211
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:01,620
Please leave.

212
00:09:15,380 --> 00:09:17,060
(Chunfeng Clinic)

213
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,530
My Lord.

214
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:22,030
