235
00:10:11,760 --> 00:10:13,450
Nonsense!

236
00:10:13,680 --> 00:10:15,250
She just got lucky.

237
00:10:16,390 --> 00:10:19,660
Ling Ruojin, let's wait and see.

238
00:10:22,190 --> 00:10:24,760
